window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Firewalkers are brave. Firewalkers are resourceful. Firewalkers are expendable.</p> <p>The Earth is burning. Nothing can survive at the Anchor, not without water and power. But the ultra-rich, waiting for their ride off the dying Earth? They can buy water. And thanks to their investment, the sun can provide power.</p> <p>But someone has to repair the solar panels when they fail, down in the deserts below.</p> <p>Kids like Mao, and Lup√©, and Hotep, kids with brains and guts but no hope. The Firewalkers.</p>"; 
